In tictactoe, the center is often considered the most strategic position because it controls multiple squares. If I take the center (1,1), then whatever I do on the other side, I can counter. For example, if I go to (0,0), I can go to (2,2) to block. Similarly, if I go to (0,2), I can go to (2,0). So taking the center gives me a strong foundation. 

